速显著高于上代集显强大性能。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/images/line_hr.png\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 900px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 20px\">技嘉超耐久5PLUS技术</div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 160px\"><img title=\"技嘉超耐久5PLUS技术\" src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/fileupload/features/2/overview/3193.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 710px\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify\"><br />\r\n技嘉首次将超耐久5 PLUS使用于技嘉Intel<sup style=\"vertical-align: text-top\">&reg;</sup>8系列主板，通过该技术带来的一系列新特性和优质元件，为用户提供更容易突破超频记录的平台，和更凉爽更高效的操作体验，并更好的延长主板寿命。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/images/line_hr.png\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div style=\"padding