ze-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">感应器类型：重力感应器，光线传感器，距离传感器<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n拍照功能&nbsp;摄像头：内置<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n摄像头类型：双摄像头（前后）<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n摄像头像素：前：30万像素，后：300万像素<br />\r\n传感器类型：Exmor R CMOS（背照式感光元件）<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n闪&nbsp; 光&nbsp; 灯：LED补光灯<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n自动对焦：支持<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n拍摄模式：正常，全景，微笑拍摄<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n图像尺寸：最大支持3264&times;2448像素照片拍摄<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n连拍功能：支持<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n定 时 器：支持<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n视频拍摄：1080p（720&times;1080，30帧/秒）视频录制<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n其它功能：拍摄时电子防抖功能</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n<strong>娱乐功能</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">视频播放：支持MP4/3GP/AVI/M2TS/TS/FLV/MOV/ASF//RMVB等格式<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n音频播放：支持MP3/AAC/M4A/MKA/AMR/WAV/MID/OGG/FLAC/APE等格式&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n图形格式：支持JPEG/PNG/GIF/BMP等格式<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\nFlash播放：支持Flash Player 10.1&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n应用特点：支持Google latitude，Google Talk&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n电子书 Java扩展</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0